{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A class which wraps all "},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"component  tokens of radio button","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":" for  "},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"radios","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" objects"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"like "},{"code":"OUDSRadioButton","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"code":"OUDSRadioButtonItem","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Contains also references to semantic tokens providers so as to be able to use them to define the component tokens."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This provider should be integrated as a "},{"code":"AllRadioButtonComponentTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation inside "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to provide all tokens to the users."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation to use."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Custom themes can use subclass of "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeRadioButtonComponentTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":" and apply the provider they need."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It implements also the protocol "},{"code":"RadioButtonComponentTokens","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to expose the component tokens for "},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"radio buttons","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" through any "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Radio buttons"}],"type":"emphasis"